"<h3 style=\" margin-top:14px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:large; font-weight:700; color:#9966c6;\">Step 9: Bankrupt Members</span></h3>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Manage bankruptcy details with the following options:</p>\n"
