"<li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Votes will be counted successfully.</li>\n"
"<li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">To stop the voting session, re-enter the passkey and click &quot;Stop&quot;.</li></ul></li></ol>\n"
